husetts]]: Cpt Archibald Hopkins\n* [[49th Pennsylvania Infantry|49th Pennsylvania]]: Bvt Col Baynton J. Hickman\n* [[82nd Pennsylvania Infantry|82nd Pennsylvania]]: Col Isaac C. Bassett\n* [[119th Pennsylvania Infantry|119th Pennsylvania]]: Ltc Gideon Clark ('''w''', April 2), Maj William C. Gray\n* [[2nd Rhode Island Infantry|2nd Rhode Island]]: Ltc [[Elisha H. Rhodes]]\n* [[5th Wisconsin Volunteer Infantry Regiment|5th Wisconsin]]: Col [[Thomas Allen (Wisconsin politician)|Thomas S. Allen]]\n|-\n| rowspan=3 |\nSecond Division\n\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBvt MG [[George W. Getty]]\n[[File:VIcorpsbadge2.png|frameless|left]]\n| 1st Brigade\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol [[James M. Warner]]\n|\n* [[62nd New York Volunteer Infantry Regiment|62nd New York]]: Ltc Theodore B. Hamilton\n* [[93rd Pennsylvania Infantry|93rd Pennsylvania]]: Col Charles W. Eckman, Cpt B. Frank Hean,<ref>In command part of April 2.</ref> Col Charles W. Eckman\n* [[98th Pennsylvania Infantry|98th Pennsylvania]]: Ltc Charles Reen ('''w''', April 2), Cpt Bernhard Gessler\n* [[102nd Pennsylvania Infantry|102nd Pennsylvania]]: Ltc James Patchell\n* [[139th Pennsylvania Infantry|139th Pennsylvania]]: Ltc John G. Parr, Maj James McGregor, Ltc John G. Parr\n|-\n| [[Vermont Brigade|2nd Brigade]]\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBvt MG [[Lewis A. Grant]] ('''w''', April 2)\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nLtc [[Amasa S. Tracy]]\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol Charles Mundee\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nLtc Amasa S. Tracy\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBvt MG Lewis A. Grant\n|\n* [[2nd Vermont Infantry|2nd Vermont]]: Ltc Amasa S. Tracy\n* [[3rd Vermont Infantry|3rd Vermont]]: Col Horace W. Floyd<ref>Commanded 3rd and 4th Vermont on March 31.</ref>\n* [[4th Vermont Infantry|4th Vermont]]: Cpt George H. Amidon\n* [[5th Vermont Infantry|5th Vermont]]: Ltc Ronald A. Kennedy\n* [[6th Vermont Infantry|6th Vermont]]: Maj William J. Sperry, Ltc Sumner H. Lincoln<ref name=\"April4\">In command from April 4.</ref>\n* [[11th Vermont Infantry|1st Vermont Heavy Ar