icut Infantry Regiment (Colored)|29th Connecticut (Colored)]]: Col William B. Wooster\n* [[9th United States Colored Infantry|9th U.S. Colored Troops]]: Col Thomas Bayley\n* 115th U.S. Colored Troops:<ref>Detached from First Brigade, Second Division.</ref> Col Robert H. Earnest\n* 117th U.S. Colored Troops: Col Lewis G. Brown\n|-\n| 3rd Brigade\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBG [[Henry Goddard Thomas|Henry G. Thomas]]\n|\n* [[19th United States Colored Infantry|19th U.S. Colored Troops]]: Col Joseph G. Perkins\n* [[23rd United States Colored Infantry|23rd U.S. Colored Troops]]: Ltc Marshall L. Dempcy\n* [[43rd United States Colored Infantry|43rd U.S. Colored Troops]]: Col Stephen B. Yeoman\n* 114th U.S. Colored Troops: Ltc Thomas D. Sedgwick\n|-\n| Attached Brigade<ref>Detached from Third Brigade, Second Division.</ref>\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBvt BG [[Charles Sawyer Russell|Charles S. Russell]]\n|\n*[[10th United States Colored Infantry|10th U.S. Colored Troops]]: Ltc Edward H. Powell\n* [[28th Regiment United States Colored Troops|28th U.S. Colored Troops]]: Ltc Thomas H. Logan\n|-\n| Cavalry\n|\n* 2nd U.S. Colored Troops Cavalry: Col George W. Cole\n|-\n| rowspan= 3 |\nSecond Division\n\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\nBG [[William Birney]]\n| 1st Brigade\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol James Shaw, Jr.\n|\n* [[7th United States Colored Infantry|7th U.S. Colored Troops]]: Ltc Oscar E. Pratt\n* 109th U.S. Colored Troops: Col Orion A. Bartholomew\n* [[116th Regiment Infantry U.S. Colored Troops|116th U.S. Colored Troops]]: Ltc George H. Laird\n|-\n| 2nd Brigade\n<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;\nCol [[Ulysses Doubleday (general)|Ulysses Doubleday]]\n|\n* [[8th United States Colored Infantry|8th U.S. Colored Troops]]: Col [[Samuel C. Armstrong]]\n*[[41st United States Colored Infantry|41st U.S. Colored Troops]]: Col Llewellyn F. Haskell\n*[[45th United States Colored Infantry Regiment|45th U.S. Colored Troops]]: Maj Theodore C. Glazier\n* [[127th United States Colored Infantry Regiment|127th U.S. Col