ie Binder]]|USA}} || Boston, United States || 21-04-1980 || \n|- \n| 18 || '''2:39:29''' ||align=left| {{flagathlete|[[Sylviane Levesque]]|FRA}} || Montataire, France || 12-10-1980 || \n|- \n| 19 || '''2:39:49''' ||align=left| {{flagathlete|[[Jane Wipf]]|USA}} || Honolulu, United States || 07-12-1980 || \n|- \n| 20 || '''2:40:35.7''' ||align=left| {{flagathlete|[[Dorthe Rasmussen]]|DEN}} || Miami, United States || 12-01-1980 || \n|- \n| 21 || '''2:41:01''' ||align=left| {{flagathlete|[[Marty Cooksey]]|USA}} || London, United Kingdom || 03-08-1980 || \n|- \n| 22 || '''2:41:14.9''' ||align=left| {{flagathlete|[[Martha Sartain]]|USA}} || Dallas, United States || 06-12-1980 || \n|- \n| 23 || '''2:41:22''' ||align=left| {{flagathlete|[[Magda Ilands]]|BEL}} || Berchem, Belgium || 12-09-1980 || \n|- \n| 24 || '''2:41:44''' ||align=left| {{flagathlete|[[Beth Guerin]]|USA}} || London, United Kingdom || 03-08-1980 || \n|- \n| 25 || '''2:41:47''' ||align=left| {{flagathlete|[[Chantal Langlac\u00e9]]|FRA}} || Montataire, France || 12-10-1980 || \n|}\n\n==References==\n*[http://digilander.libero.it/Mennea/Stagionali/WRL/1980/Mar.htm digilander.libero]\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.arrs.run/MaraRank/ATM_Mara1980.htm 1980 Marathon Ranking] by the ARRS\n\n{{Marathon}}\n{{Footer WBYP Marathon Men}}\n{{Footer WBYP Marathon Women}}\n\n[[Category:Marathon running by year|1980]]\n[[Category:1980 in athletics (track and field)| Marathon]]\n", "text_old": "{{Disputed|date=June 2010}}\n\nThis page lists the '''World Best Year Performances''' in the year '''[[1980 in athletics (track and field)|1980]]''' in the '''[[marathon race|Marathon]]''' for both men and women. One of the main events during this season were the [[Athletics at the 1980 Summer Olympics|1980 Summer Olympics]] in [[Moscow]], [[Soviet Union]], where the final of the [[Athletics at the 1980 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's marathon|men's competition]] was held on Friday August 1, 1980. The competition had an